"The minimum size for this partition is ${MINSIZE} (or ${PERCENT}) and its "
"maximum size is ${MAXSIZE}."
msgstr ""
"Y maint lleiaf ar gyfer y rhaniad hwn yw ${MINSIZE} (neu ${PERCENT}) a'r "
"maint mwyaf yw ${MAXSIZE}."

